WEBVTT

1
00:00:04.133 --> 00:00:06.066
The Emperor seems to be in a good mood.

2
00:00:06.266 --> 00:00:07.800
Is there some good news?

3
00:00:07.800 --> 00:00:11.633
I have something to discuss with the Empress Dowager today.

4
00:00:11.766 --> 00:00:15.066
What’s the matter? The harem has not yet established an empress.

5
00:00:15.800 --> 00:00:17.166
Concubine Rong has a noble lineage.

6
00:00:17.166 --> 00:00:18.266
She is virtuous and gentle.

7
00:00:18.366 --> 00:00:20.000
If she had not cared for me attentively,

8
00:00:20.133 --> 00:00:21.666
I wouldn’t have recovered so quickly.

9
00:00:21.800 --> 00:00:22.600
I

10
00:00:23.366 --> 00:00:24.666
want to make Concubine Rong the Empress.

11
00:00:24.733 --> 00:00:26.600
What’s wrong with that?

12
00:00:26.700 --> 00:00:28.700
Her promotion has been too rapid.

13
00:00:28.900 --> 00:00:31.000
Both the court and the harem have reservations.

14
00:00:31.166 --> 00:00:32.066
With Prince Duan’s death,

15
00:00:32.066 --> 00:00:33.066
the situation is set.

16
00:00:33.333 --> 00:00:35.600
I still need their approval to establish an empress.

17
00:00:35.700 --> 00:00:38.000
You must understand, Emperor,

18
00:00:38.133 --> 00:00:39.900
the Empress is crucial to the nation’s fortune.

19
00:00:39.900 --> 00:00:41.366
It cannot be decided hastily.

20
00:00:42.366 --> 00:00:44.400
Though Su Shi has indeed served you well,

21
00:00:44.466 --> 00:00:46.000
appointing him as Empress recklessly

22
00:00:46.000 --> 00:00:47.833
will surely bring disaster to Su Shi.

23
00:00:48.100 --> 00:00:49.366
Quickly retract your decision.

24
00:00:49.366 --> 00:00:50.666
This matter is not to be taken lightly.

25
00:00:50.666 --> 00:00:51.866
Punish them as needed.

26
00:00:51.900 --> 00:00:53.266
Emperor, please return first.

27
00:01:05.700 --> 00:01:07.400
I’m here again.

28
00:01:07.533 --> 00:01:09.566
Last time it was granted by the Empress Dowager.

29
00:01:09.866 --> 00:01:11.300
This time it’s the Emperor.

30
00:01:12.133 --> 00:01:14.000
Such a damnable sense of fate.

31
00:01:15.166 --> 00:01:16.866
What a grand palace, Your Highness.

32
00:01:17.066 --> 00:01:19.933
Oh no, now it’s Your Highness the Noble Consort.

33
00:01:19.933 --> 00:01:21.766
This servant pays respects to Noble Consort.

34
00:01:21.866 --> 00:01:24.400
Noble Consort, may you have peace and prosperity.

35
00:01:25.933 --> 00:01:27.300
Your Highness, rest assured.

36
00:01:27.333 --> 00:01:30.100
This servant will do her utmost to take care of you.

37
00:01:30.300 --> 00:01:32.233
This damned sense of destiny.

38
00:01:33.000 --> 00:01:35.466
It seems next time it will be the Kun Ning Palace.
